{"tid":2342501,"cid":8,"subCid":0,"title":"[狂賀] 「鬼滅之刃」打敗「千與千尋」成為日本影史冠軍","createTime":"2020-12-27T07:40:03.000Z","updateTime":"2020-12-27T13:22:46.000Z","uid":76637,"like":8,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"3991e7fb1bc3c991bd60b7d6cde559f8fe851cb9","tid":2342501,"uid":76637,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-27T07:40:03.000Z","msg":"「鬼滅之刃劇場版 無限列車篇」自從今年10月上映以來氣勢如虹，不僅在全台票房突破5.7億穩坐冠軍，<strong><span class=\"xx-large\"><span class=\"red\">今日票房更衝破317億日元</span></span></strong>（約新台幣88.76億元），打破宮崎駿「神隱少女」的316.8億日元（約新台幣88.7億元），榮登日本影史票房冠軍。<br />\n<br />\n電影在台上映至今，也已5.7億票房穩坐2020年台灣票房冠軍，台灣12月31日將上映4DX版本，上映影城包含台北信義威秀影城、林口MITSUI OUTLET PARK威秀影城、新竹大遠百威秀影城、台南大遠百威秀影城、高雄大遠百威秀影城。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://stars.udn.com/star/story/10090/5123906\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstars.udn.com%2Fstar%2Fstory%2F10090%2F5123906&d=sZqGLlkYYIxatccyfr7NWPtobIAPz7vP9zHpdy2ENqg%3D&h=de7c579e\" target=\"_blank\">https://stars.udn.com/star/story/10090/5123906</a>"},{"pid":"d8279f8ef4eedfdc8573fee50174de57b936856b","tid":2342501,"uid":186,"like":5,"dislike":1,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-27T07:46:35.000Z","msg":"千與千尋沒有輸"},{"pid":"ac2a1075b932ba3e16b0f274d31d0787083c4bd2","tid":2342501,"uid":299548,"like":3,"dislike":1,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-27T07:47:23.000Z","msg":"宮崎先生沒有輸<img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/wail_r.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/wail_r.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/wail_r.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f3689e9941ce990194d9d51431db84e053a1db96","tid":2342501,"uid":127425,"like":2,"dislike":3,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-27T07:47:24.000Z","msg":"千與千尋已成傳奇<br />\n唔需要票房黎證明自己既地位"},{"pid":"9f57bcb2f31298d133b0b68cdaf8fa1e35cbc635","tid":2342501,"uid":373119,"like":1,"dislike":4,"score":-3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-12-27T07:54:27.000Z","msg":"想知個票房有無計埋通漲個啲<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" 